        "creativity_and_innovation": 5,
        "pitch_and_presentation": 6
    },

    "final_verdict": "TalentBud shows promise as a recruitment tool but requires significant refinement to reach its full potential. Recommendations: 1) Implement stronger security and privacy measures, 2) Develop the video/audio integration features as originally planned, 3) Conduct and document pilot programs with actual HR departments, 4) Add more innovative features to differentiate from existing solutions, 5) Create clear metrics for measuring success and ROI. The project scores 6/10 overall, showing good foundation but needing improvements in key areas to become a competitive solution in the HR tech market."
